{"tid":639113,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呀倫敦人妻先生，香港人嘅架畀你丟晒！","createTime":"2018-04-23T08:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T10:55:44.000Z","uid":166571,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"20a391205881abbab3484c2e0ff859dc5a1cc60b","tid":639113,"uid":166571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:54:08.000Z","msg":"紙袋都貪，人哋唔畀仲要diu9人！肉酸唔肉酸呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/165014_b43fa9c69a8bde70dd19f39df12cc8bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F165014_b43fa9c69a8bde70dd19f39df12cc8bf.jpg&h=41a96891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>餅店拒借紙袋　KOL發千字文鬧爆　惹網民公憤</strong><br />\n手提紙袋拎拎下爛咗，你會點做？有網絡作家日前欲向連鎖餅店相借紙袋，誰料遭職員一口拒絕，遂發貼寸爆餅店，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「啲紙袋留番畀你哋煲醋啦！」</span></strong>惟其「公審」行逕卻未獲網民支持。<br />\n<br />\n該網絡作家周日（22日）在其社交專頁發貼，指當日到尖沙咀一大型商場購物期間，手提紙袋突然破爛，東西散落一地，狼狽不堪，遂走到旁邊一間連鎖餅店詢問︰「唔好意思，可以借我一個紙袋嗎」？<br />\n<br />\n據貼文指，當時店員面帶不悅，並以一句「無喎」拒絕。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>發貼者形容自己猶如被驅趕的乞丐，是種「侮辱」。<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n他解釋，自己非因借袋不果而生氣，而是不滿店員的態度︰「你可以答『公司policy（規定）要買野（嘢）先俾（畀）袋』，咁我咪買囉」、「家陣香港地邊個俾（畀）唔起幾十蚊」、「你駛（使）唔駛（使）咁樣嘅態度講野（嘢）呀」？<br />\n<br />\n他覺得店員稱無紙袋是敷衍他︰<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「大佬，你啲客買完Cake（蛋糕）好似非洲人咁捧上頭頂行架（㗎）？」他指自己曾多次在該餅店中環分店購物，「我邊次買Cake冇袋？我課足你班粉X一年金呀」！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n他最後明言，發貼原意並非要求任何補償，寸爆餅店<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「唔好諗住送個蛋糕過黎（嚟）（賠禮），我當你面扔去餵狗」。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n紙袋風波鬧大，貼文一日內有逾千次回應，惟不少網民均認為該網絡作家「小事化大」︰「一個紙袋就買起你人格」，「無啦啦借紙袋，完全零消費又講到自己買左（咗）野（嘢）咁」。有人則認為，膠袋稅實施後，當局人員會不時「放蛇」，因此不少店員對「袋」都非常敏感，嘆謂「互相體諒下，世界更美好」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180423/bkn-20180423162553466-0423_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180423%2Fbkn-20180423162553466-0423_00822_001.html&d=wH3wEsOnesGP%2BWOuAQRlR54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=8f91078a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180423/bkn-20180423162553466-0423_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n原Post在此 (P.S. 人妻先生好似block晒留言嘅人 小9器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mrwifelondon/photos/a.356470398065890.1073741828.355077994871797/573702413009353/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmrwifelondon%2Fphotos%2Fa.356470398065890.1073741828.355077994871797%2F573702413009353%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=wH3wEsOnesGP%2BWOuAQRlR54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=42e1d7e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mrwifelondon/photos/a.356470398065890.1073741828.355077994871797/573702413009353/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/165348_6062afa8d63b7ff27fcb0fe683a70369.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F165348_6062afa8d63b7ff27fcb0fe683a70369.JPG&h=8d476b47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa270005a5d884db888d709702bdcfa88068b47b","tid":639113,"uid":91463,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:06:58.000Z","msg":"咩page黎, 聽都未撚聽過"},{"pid":"18e81ed7534b9006d9bac7b93524b9653db3bb80","tid":639113,"uid":34468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:09:45.000Z","msg":"仲諗係人妻定先生<br />\n原來係基佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44bfe664a4a6f59783bea41f769e64d37ab3c558","tid":639113,"uid":166571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa270005a5d884db888d709702bdcfa88068b47b","tid":639113,"uid":91463,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:06:58.000Z","msg":"咩page黎, 聽都未撚聽過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"「既是人妻，也是先生；我八婆所以